reviews.reviewText: Was very happy with quality and product!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on May 18, 2021
reviews.reviewText: I just got a 24 oz hydro flask and was looking for a straw lid on the hydro flask website and found out they don't make any for smaller sizes ;( Bought this one hoping it would work and it definitely does. It's so easy to drink through especially with the detachable straw that comes with it. I was worried that it would make a loud slurping noise as some other straw lids do, but this one is almost completely silent. Only negative I have about this is that the handle isn't as comfortable to hold as the original screw-on lid, but it's worth not having to take 10 seconds to screw the lid off every time you want a drink. For the price, this lid is definitely worth it!!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on July 16, 2021
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars Loop gets in the way
reviews.reviewText: Enables drinking without removing the lid, which was my objective. However I don't want to use (and have to clean) the straws and figured I could just tip the bottle back and drink, but the loop on the lid (which is hard plastic and not soft) will hit your nose. If you are planning to suck the drink up by using the straws I'm sure the lid will work fine. I'm not really happy with the design for my use and am planning to replace this lid with one where the loop pivots out of the way.
My youngest daughter is very happy with her purchase. Come with 2 straws
Great quality, doesn't leak and nice to drink out of.
